		<title>10Fords</title>
		<content>Fords was opened in 1968. In 1972 they 
built the office blocks.               
Ford employs 1400 people, 60% live in  
Daventry 40% live within a 15 mile     
radius of Daventry.                    
Fords is 18000 square feet or the size 
of 23 Wembley pitches and is the       
biggest single storey building in      
Europe.                                
Fords deal with places all over the    
world at some time or another.         
Fords will  probably be doing the same 
business in ten years time because of  
inreased competition from other        
countries.                             
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
